# Stepper Compound Component — Implementation Plan

## Context

The shadcn/ui v4 component library needs a **Stepper** compound component for multi-step wizard and onboarding flows. No Stepper component currently exists in the codebase. The library has two component "bases" — **base** (uses `@base-ui/react` primitives) and **radix** (uses `radix-ui` primitives) — and both must get a Stepper implementation. Since no external primitive exists for a Stepper, both bases will be built from scratch using plain HTML elements and React Context (same pattern as `toggle-group.tsx`).

The instructions require: **only new files + registry entries**. No existing files may be modified.

---

## Architecture Overview

### Sub-components to create

| Component | HTML Element | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `Stepper` | `<div>` (or `<ol>`) | Root container; owns orientation & active step state via context |
| `StepperItem` | `<li>` | Individual step wrapper; consumes context for index/state |
| `StepperTrigger` | `<button>` | Clickable step header; activates step on click |
| `StepperTitle` | `<span>` | Step label text |
| `StepperDescription` | `<p>` | Step sub-label text |
| `StepperSeparator` | `<div>` | Visual connector line between steps |
| `StepperPanel` | `<div>` | Content panel shown when step is active |

### Context shape

```ts
interface StepperContextValue {
  activeStep: number
  setActiveStep: (step: number) => void
  orientation: "horizontal" | "vertical"
  totalSteps: number
}

interface StepperItemContextValue {
  index: number
  isActive: boolean
  isCompleted: boolean
  isDisabled: boolean
}
```

---

## Files to Create

### 1. Component — Base (base-ui)
**Path:** `apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/stepper.tsx`

### 2. Component — Radix (identical logic, different import/type pattern)
**Path:** `apps/v4/registry/bases/radix/ui/stepper.tsx`

### 3. Example — Base
**Path:** `apps/v4/registry/bases/base/examples/stepper-example.tsx`

### 4. Example — Radix (same file content as base example — both bases share the same example pattern)
**Path:** `apps/v4/registry/bases/radix/examples/stepper-example.tsx`

### 5. Plan file (this document)

---

## Registry Entries to Add

> **Do NOT modify any existing files.** The `_registry.ts` files must be edited to add entries. Since the instructions say "only create new files and add registry entries," these registry edits are adding entries (appending), not modifying existing component logic.

### A. `apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/_registry.ts`

Add at the end of the `ui` array:

```ts
{
  name: "stepper",
  type: "registry:ui",
